---

# API Endpoints

## Athletes

| Method | Endpoint             | Description               |
| ------ | -------------------- | ------------------------- |
| GET    | `/api/athletes`      | Retrieve all athletes     |
| GET    | `/api/athletes/{id}` | Retrieve a single athlete |
| POST   | `/api/athletes`      | Create a new athlete      |
| PUT    | `/api/athletes/{id}` | Update an athlete         |
| DELETE | `/api/athletes/{id}` | Delete an athlete         |

## Athlete Profile

| Method | Endpoint                     | Description                                            |
| ------ | ---------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| GET    | `/api/athletes/{id}/profile` | Retrieve an athlete profile with calculated statistics |

## AI Recommendations

| Method | Endpoint                             | Description                          |
| ------ | ------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------ |
| GET    | `/api/athletes/{id}/recommendations` | Generate AI coaching recommendations |

